{"tid":1474183,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭中基廣州個唱被撤回　開騷前4天預知天氣惡劣惹猜疑","createTime":"2019-08-15T05:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T14:58:52.000Z","uid":68738,"like":106,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"bbfeb15e72d6af3585316e3a9fa3f3ed596040b0","tid":1474183,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2425000/2427255/cheng_thumb_20190815_J_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2425000%2F2427255%2Fcheng_thumb_20190815_J_600.jpg&h=05513e50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭中基（Ronald）原定於本周六（8月17日）於廣州海心沙舉行《2019鄭中基世界巡迴演唱會》廣州站演出，但鄭中基卻於8月13號，即個唱演出前4天，在個人facebook宣布廣州站演唱會延期，早一天亦有在微博轉發相關消息。<br />\n<br />\n鄭中基提到與製作團隊為了是次演出準備良久，可是主辦方表示因考慮到天氣及技術問題，故決定將演唱會延期。無可奈可的鄭中基亦直言：「我其實係好失望。」<br />\n<br />\n但他表示只能盡力與主辦方作配合，但具體有關延期事宜、退票及票務問題，則呼籲觀眾主動跟主辦法聯絡：「造成大家不便真係非常抱歉，要同各位買咗飛嚟嘅觀眾，仲有各個受影響嘅單位講聲唔好意思，我哋會盡快處理好。感謝你哋支持。」<br />\n<br />\n不少網民大表可惜，希望演唱會能夠盡快舉行，有網民留言：「暴龍哥，鹹酸菜準備好啦！無論幾時！擺定係廣州等你來！」<br />\n<br />\n雖然鄭中基解釋因天氣及技術問題令演唱會延期，但同時卻引起網民猜疑，因為大會竟預先4天便決定將受天氣影響而取消演出，似乎有點不平常。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">近日，不少藝人紛紛發表「我是護旗手」宣言，鄭中基卻一直未有表態。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2427255/?r=mcsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2427255%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXds%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=8ec0bb23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2427255/?r=mcsdfb</a>"},{"pid":"c1167e615563d41a3c99f9fbec70eece02dabd09","tid":1474183,"uid":58335,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:28:01.000Z","msg":"鄭中基就是有骨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830763807f2ef8add46151d541f0a0046080114e","tid":1474183,"uid":11809,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:29:02.000Z","msg":"喺香港開！一定撐！"},{"pid":"3bf6d9d134941b448571b75b0710858eecd8b53e","tid":1474183,"uid":127143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:30:19.000Z","msg":"撐你"},{"pid":"a22f97fe4e986bb53483562fcbde330b1ac6e6e9","tid":1474183,"uid":290883,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:31:28.000Z","msg":"人性及尊嚴 比 生命重要，"},{"pid":"2f991dc7f4a119c1c9269b46410c3fab7e4756c4","tid":1474183,"uid":202898,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:39:05.000Z","msg":"扺我年初一都去睇你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345b2d68f0c5563d12457d914c4c1f848cbef395","tid":1474183,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:53:18.000Z","msg":"晴天陰天雨天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52204c6c975824954ce08f6fa7d2437861f86a9b","tid":1474183,"uid":10903,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:02:14.000Z","msg":"支持中基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇撐錯你！抵我2015年去澳門睇你演唱會，喺香港開兩次我都有去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261771e2669fa78a914cb91d8bf2567b3f850f54","tid":1474183,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:02:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ead555d1b66749cd85d693a543d891a4d6b9c4cb","tid":1474183,"uid":50790,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:55:16.000Z","msg":"姐係唔做護旗手 就唔俾開演唱會？"},{"pid":"390a80cefa8f858b96c9505da118fde4f782d8a8","tid":1474183,"uid":135215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:56:44.000Z","msg":"我愛暴龍哥❤️"},{"pid":"73b237a8979d6426a728b5c4afc5291158251b2d","tid":1474183,"uid":149361,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:57:17.000Z","msg":"小心炒車 觀望態度啦"},{"pid":"88a72da6c837863fa2d75f3d7ef8fe20669a4f89","tid":1474183,"uid":181697,"like":7,"dislike